Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel you're the first friend\Nthat I have ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[both exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Misa.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you ask Rem
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Light to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know we could be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all I ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill L for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] L will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,WAGER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Rem] So, when should I kill him?\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take me to where he is,\NI can kill him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I should think this through\Nbefore we do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need tonight to decide\Nhow we're going to kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you my answer tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Also, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't kill him until I give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] All right. I'll promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At least where L is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, I need you to give me\Nyour cellphone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,About time! What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me yours too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Misa, I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your girlfriend!\NI should have your number.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you,\NI'm under surveillance by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind, it's not difficult for them\Nto bug even cellphones these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, what about this?\NI'll just give you one of my phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up with three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I use them for different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use yours, I think we'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! I can hear your voice\Nevery day, and text you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll keep this one turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the only one making the calls,\Nand only when it's absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when are you gonna call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Probably tomorrow.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That will most likely be the day\Nwe execute L,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll call you either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't sound like a very romantic call
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I suppose we can always\Ntalk about us afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you should probably\Ngo home now, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But why? It's only seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The time for lovers\Nis just beginning, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go for a romantic dinner,\Nthen maybe a moonlight stroll in the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and after that, the main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Misa.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckling] Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, when you're talking to Rem outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,be careful that no one's around to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I always do with Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye! Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Misa! Come again real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]\NThat kiss came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Sure. It's very important\Nthat Misa stays infatuated with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I need to decide\Nif L should die tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he hasn't gone public yet,\Nif Ryuga dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the other Task Force members\Nwill be suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to make sure I'm prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought perhaps you were hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because he said he thinks of you\Nas a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] A friend?\NI just gave him what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From the start, I've said\Nif it's my friendship he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give it to him\Nas a way to win his trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuga and Light Yagami\Nappear to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But L is Kira's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's right.\NRyuga revealed that he is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have him die in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,chances are that less people\Nwill suspect I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if they do, there'd be no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only speculate\Nwhat will happen after he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be L's,\Nor at least Ryuga and Ryuzaki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,last day alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[L sniffs] Snack crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Yagami.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die within the next few days,\Nyour son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, another hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.\NWhat are you talking about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to me, I have asked\NWatari to make himself available to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm counting on you, team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he was almost cleared,\Nand now this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, how much do you suspect my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, the truth is, I don't even know\Nwhat to think anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been in a situation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira and the Second Kira\Nare working together right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,things are not looking good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be thinking\Nas clearly as I normally do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[slurps loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I still consider him a suspect\Nonly because we don't have anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,if I do happen to be killed soon,\Nplease assume that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[all grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I have no choice\Nbut to make a sneak attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all a wager now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds twittering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light chuckles] I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know how to get by, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hey, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi, could we continue this later?\NI need a moment alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she's not upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. Is it okay to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you were afraid\Nto appear in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did. But then I realized\Nthat as long as you're not Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is, you're the only one\Non the outside who knows me as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the unlikely event\Nthat I die in the next few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've instructed your father\Nand everyone at headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to assume that you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you told me yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that you missed having me around\Nat school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured, why not come back\Nfor a little change of pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it doesn't kill me,\Ncollege is a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I have to admit,\Nwithout you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligent conversation\Nis hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[L chuckles] I see. Luckily,\NKiyomi's there to fill the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Now I don't know.\NIs it still okay to kill him today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No. As soon as I make the decision\Nto kill him, he suddenly appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as if to distract me from my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's trying to guarantee\Nhis safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way things are,\NI'm playing right into his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you want to have some cake\Nwith me in the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I have a break now anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's perfect.\NI'm kinda craving shortcake right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's hope they have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Light! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a photo-shoot nearby,\Nso I thought I'd come by to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Misa, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this must be a friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks so different. Unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa will be able to see\NRyuga's real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there. I'm Light's girlfriend,\NMisa Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hideki Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he has the exact same\Nfirst and last name
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,as the famous idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty bizarre, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] But it's different\Nthan the name I'm seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuga,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding to come here today\Nwas a mistake. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell is he laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it mean he noticed something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If he somehow guessed\Nthat she's the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way he'd be laughing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been a huge fan of yours\Never since the August issue of Eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? That's so sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Oh my God,\Nisn't that girl Misa-Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl] She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I should've guessed I'd be spotted\Nwith all these kids around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, like, your biggest fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Couldn't do it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Somebody just touched my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an outrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of this situation\Nis unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find whoever\Nis responsible for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ryuga, you're so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-I want to touch her too.\N-Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask Misa what L's real name\Nis as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but all these people are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time! Or were you planning\Nto be late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm sorry, Yoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go!\N-Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Misa's away from the crowd,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to give her a call\Nand ask for L's real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Light! I'll see you after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss you already. [giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, perhaps we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, could you go on ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay then. I'll see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been fun… L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that I was the one\Nto discover your name
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] L, it's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that I was the one\Nto discover your name
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[pop music ringtone playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ ringtone continues playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Hello"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that you, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess someone must have\Ndropped this phone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of the commotion earlier on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He took it. Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah.\NThat's Misa's cellphone you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-I can give it back to her.\N-I see. Sure, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably thinks he's pretty clever\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Misa has another phone\Nhe doesn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just call that one instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Oh, this time\Nit's actually my cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's done then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly sure how you'll take this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but regarding Misa Amane,\Nthere's something you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken her into custody\Nunder suspicion of being the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] How long has he known about Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\Nhe'd find her this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We gathered physical evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from the envelopes that were sent\Nby the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular,\Nwe recovered hairs and fibers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from the masking tape used to seal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They matched what we found in Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be a public uproar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,if it gets out that she's been apprehended\Nas the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, officially, we've charged her manager\Nwith drug possession
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's a voluntary witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt any of this would get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The videos...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have destroyed all the evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,before the police had a chance\Nto go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end,\NRyuga knew that his best defense
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was to stay close to me\Nrather than trying to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He confronted things head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This wager was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Was my…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-No!\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The real battle is just beginning, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Watari, has she said anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] No, she hasn't spoken a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me a visual of her, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Ryuzaki!\NWhat's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I've apprehended her on suspicion\Nof being the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances are Amane is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be enough evidence\Nto convict her, but all the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there can be no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we need a confession out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to know how she kills,\Nwhether she knows Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and, if so, who he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, take the necessary precautions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but beyond that, you're free to do\Nwhatever has to be done, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make her speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] Oh, and Mr. Yagami?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Light has now become our prime suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm probably gonna bring him in\Nfor interrogation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, be prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Ryuzaki, Amane is talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Quickly, get me a visual and audio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting and grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Finally,\Nafter three days of this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me. Please, just kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, maybe this was all too much\Nfor a young girl to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. We've pushed her too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[L, distorted voice]\NMisa Amane, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just kill me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you admit\Nto being the Second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the reason you wish to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] No! I don't know anything\Nabout the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to, you could kill me\Nright now, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, do you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore. Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this, then Light Yagami dies too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't. No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to die for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't kill me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop her!\NWatari, don't let her bite her tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[all grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that this behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,could be attributed to Kira\Ncontrolling her actions before death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa has refused my offer\Nto help her escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt because she knows\Nit would cause you trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,since the police would then have\Nproof of her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When her suffering became more\Nthan she could bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she started begging me to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this because she wants you\Nto love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not possibly\Nlet it go on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only one way\Nto save her from her suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Forfeiting ownership of the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If Misa forfeits ownership\Nof the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,all her memories related to it\Nwould disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All the murders she committed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All those memories would be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your secret would be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Misa would no longer\Nbe able to see Ryuk or me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,SEVERAL HOURS EARLIER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When this is done, you'll forget\Neverything about Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa, muffled speech]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The human being who you love\Nis Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise those feelings will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,forfeit ownership of the Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave everything to Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Misa is no longer\Nthe owner of the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the right thing, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was beginning to think that was\Nthe only way out of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If her memories of the Death Note\Nare gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then chances are they'll have\Nto release her eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I proposed this to Misa\Nknowing it was exactly what you wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it would serve your purposes.
